window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Winter came and so did the war.</b></p> <p>After breaking taboos and confronting the goddesses in order to save Lilith, Sol is given no time to breath as he need to be ready for what will represent his first step towards conquering the world—fighting Wratharis, the Kingdom of Beastmen.</p> <p>From alliances with the witches of Salem to manipulating the elves with the help of Nefertiti, or the Denons with Pandora, his schedule will be filled.</p>"; 
